Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,--------------op--------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.29,0:00:06.38,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}確かな想いを伝えたくて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.82,0:00:18.20,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}戻らない時間に溺れぬように
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.59,0:00:21.94,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}今を抱きしめよう
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.09,0:00:28.82,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}その微笑みを行ったり来たり　そばにいたくて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.03,0:00:36.53,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}この手を伸ばす　先には何が待ってるんだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.75,0:00:42.66,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}終わらない物語の向こう　飛び立て
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.90,0:00:47.47,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}本当の気持ちでたどり着く場所へと
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.71,0:00:51.46,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}心の翼を広げて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.76,0:00:58.47,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}廻りゆくメッセージ　幸せは胸にあるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.55,0:01:02.07,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}あと少しの勇気　涙も必要なの
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.26,0:01:06.29,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}強くなれるチャンスかもね
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.42,0:01:12.89,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}温もりのリフレイン　この大切をずっと守りたい
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.98,0:01:16.66,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}心を重ねてく　絆を感じてる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.77,0:01:20.56,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}誰も一人じゃないんだから
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.82,0:01:29.62,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}同じ空の下　確かな想いを伝えたくて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.29,0:00:06.38,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}這份真情實感　好想將它傳遞
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.82,0:00:18.20,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}為了不沉溺於一去不返的過去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.59,0:00:21.94,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}緊緊擁抱今天吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.09,0:00:28.82,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}深陷於那微笑之中　好想相伴在你的左右
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.03,0:00:36.53,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}伸出手　前方應該有什麼正等待著吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.75,0:00:42.66,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}朝著那未完結的故事　飛奔而去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.90,0:00:47.47,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}懷著一顆真誠的心向著那千難萬險之地
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.71,0:00:51.46,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}張開心靈的翅膀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.76,0:00:58.47,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}循環傳遞著一個訊息　幸福就存於這胸中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.55,0:01:02.07,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}接下來的少許勇氣　儘管須以眼淚相佐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.26,0:01:06.29,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}但這或許正是變強的契機
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.42,0:01:12.89,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}溫暖的迭句　想要永遠將這份珍重守護
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.98,0:01:16.66,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}彼此心緒交織　感受著這其中的羈絆
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.77,0:01:20.56,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}所以說沒有人是孤身隻影的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.82,0:01:29.62,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}同一片藍天下　好想將這份真情實感傳遞
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,--------------ed--------------
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.57,0:22:19.57,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}心の奥集めた　今日の光を持って
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.22,0:22:28.36,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}飛び込んだ未知の先　何が待ってるのかな
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.65,0:22:37.70,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}未来への共鳴　想い出に重ねれば
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.90,0:22:46.74,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}勇気になる　強さになる　一人じゃないから
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.93,0:22:49.05,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}（聴かせて）
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.14,0:22:57.67,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}明日もきっと会えるね　本当の笑顔で行こう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.86,0:23:06.55,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}夢見る夜明けを　一緒に迎えたい
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.72,0:23:15.73,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}無限の時間よりも　瞬間を駆け抜けよう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.98,0:23:26.93,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)}その夢の声いつか聴かせてね　信じてく
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.57,0:22:19.57,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}懷揣著內心深處收集好了的今天的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.22,0:22:28.36,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}躍入未知的前方　那裡有什麼正等待著我們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.65,0:22:37.70,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}若是與未來共鳴　不斷憶起今天的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.90,0:22:46.74,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}就會生出勇氣　就能變得堅強　也就不再是獨自一人了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.93,0:22:49.05,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}（讓你傾聽）
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.14,0:22:57.67,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}明天也一定會與你相遇　我會帶著真誠的笑容前去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.86,0:23:06.55,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}好想和你一起迎接夢想中的黎明
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.72,0:23:15.73,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}與其坐擁這無限的時刻　倒不如追趕那絢爛的瞬間
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.98,0:23:26.93,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)}相信我　總有一天會讓你傾聽那夢中的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,--------------正文--------------
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.86,0:01:39.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  好冷啊  好冷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.74,0:01:42.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是  大早上起來就這麼多牢騷的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.86,0:01:45.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷就是冷  有啥不對的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.71,0:01:47.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是說也不會變暖和的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.86,0:01:54.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我來做一些熱乎的小點心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.37,0:01:56.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天反正中午學校就放學了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.80,0:01:58.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.09,0:02:01.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太狡猾了！太狡猾了！只有春香你最狡猾！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.31,0:02:03.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃  就算你這麼說…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.57,0:02:05.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我今天也決定中午就放學回家
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.33,0:02:08.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰願意一天都待在學校
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.13,0:02:12.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨你的便
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.19,0:02:14.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說  不要無視！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.98,0:02:18.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  搬家嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.65,0:02:23.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊是啊  聽說今天隔壁會有新的鄰居搬來住
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.62,0:02:24.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.77,0:02:29.77,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}第3碗  招待的夜晚悄悄來臨
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.33,0:02:31.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.46,0:02:32.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.14,0:02:45.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是冷酷無情的學校呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.78,0:02:48.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要說得那麼事不關己啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.20,0:02:50.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這怎麼可能做的完啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.36,0:02:53.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寒假這才剛剛結束
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.33,0:02:55.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就突然佈置這麼多家庭作業
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.99,0:03:00.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  也就是說要培養蠢貨的話  只能靠數量來培養了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.78,0:03:04.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真是越來越討厭學習了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.75,0:03:08.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我剛才婉轉的表達看起來不夠明瞭？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.67,0:03:10.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃  誒  你說什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.01,0:03:14.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過說起來  這的確是很多
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.48,0:03:20.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種時候我們大家要齊心協力
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.28,0:03:23.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個人要完成的話的確很困難
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.06,0:03:24.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是大家一起來的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.11,0:03:26.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個主意或許不錯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.61,0:03:28.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼一來  集合地點就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.79,0:03:35.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我家嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.16,0:03:35.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是如此！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.07,0:03:38.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋你家真是無比舒適呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.48,0:03:41.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說你還真是特地來享受舒適的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.54,0:03:45.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因為是茶室  所以我們準備留宿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.57,0:03:47.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要擅自作決定啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.71,0:03:48.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼就這麼定了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.19,0:03:51.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起來完成的話  很快就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.40,0:03:52.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要突然做決定啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.08,0:03:54.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說今天就要來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.66,0:03:55.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝  南同學
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.39,0:04:08.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  我就先回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.24,0:04:09.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好啊  回家社團的人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.94,0:04:11.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有社團活動真是不走運呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.11,0:04:13.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是辛苦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.60,0:04:15.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回家是打掃屋子還是洗衣服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.15,0:04:18.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…先洗衣服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.18,0:04:20.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  螃蟹？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.84,0:04:21.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.80,0:04:23.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個季節  牡蠣也是很不錯的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.12,0:04:26.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是最基本的我還是覺得應該是雞肉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.87,0:04:27.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.88,0:04:29.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃  你在說什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.85,0:04:33.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說到寒冷時節的樂趣  那必然是火鍋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.89,0:04:35.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不錯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.25,0:04:39.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都帶上神秘道具  關燈之後一起扔到鍋裡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.36,0:04:43.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使夾起來抹布也一定要吃下去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.18,0:04:46.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個就稍微有點那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.86,0:04:48.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次我們來嘗試一下吧  火鍋聚會
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.33,0:04:50.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼就試試看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.58,0:04:51.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  說不定很好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.69,0:04:55.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火鍋嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.77,0:04:59.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南春香喜歡火鍋嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.43,0:05:03.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說我和南春香中間隔著一個火鍋嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.07,0:05:07.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後我們都汗流浹背
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.20,0:05:11.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後我幫南春香擦汗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.47,0:05:13.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後南春香把我的汗…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.91,0:05:19.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會…感冒的哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.88,0:05:23.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好噁心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.47,0:05:40.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新來的鄰居  看起來搬家好辛苦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.15,0:05:57.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼這個世界如此不公平
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.93,0:05:59.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.25,0:06:15.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您好  初次見面  我是南
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.96,0:06:23.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡哪裡  我們才是請您多多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.92,0:06:32.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂～
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.61,0:06:34.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.85,0:06:38.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很疼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.73,0:06:39.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰讓你無視我們
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.08,0:06:43.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天不能去玩  有好多作業要完成呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.61,0:06:46.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？一班也是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.44,0:06:47.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二班也是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.88,0:06:48.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也一起來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.05,0:06:49.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.71,0:06:50.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不知道為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.03,0:06:53.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是要在我們家完成作業
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.41,0:06:54.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也一起來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.21,0:06:56.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.66,0:06:59.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人越多越有趣嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.90,0:07:01.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要認錯目標喲！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.59,0:07:02.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僅僅是寫作業而已
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.00,0:07:04.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,記得帶上睡衣喲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.44,0:07:06.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要在那裡過夜的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.64,0:07:07.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要弄錯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.08,0:07:09.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目的只是完成作業而已
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.56,0:07:15.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.94,0:07:19.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  告訴你個好消息
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.05,0:07:21.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說會有轉校生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.92,0:07:25.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男生還是女生？去哪個班級？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.30,0:07:26.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.66,0:07:28.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是沒用的廢物
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.98,0:07:31.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然是好事  那就去調查
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.38,0:07:34.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好冷淡的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.89,0:07:45.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我吃飽啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.54,0:07:47.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.20,0:07:49.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實為口腹之歡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.83,0:07:54.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以就是這樣  大家決定在一起寫作業
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.94,0:07:58.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起寫作業似乎感覺很有趣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.01,0:08:01.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  雖然說一半成分是被逼的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.09,0:08:07.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  叫四五個人左右可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.60,0:08:08.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？家裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.07,0:08:09.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.08,0:08:12.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都是會帶睡衣來的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.35,0:08:15.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶睡衣來的話  是說要住在這裡過夜嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.62,0:08:16.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.33,0:08:19.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝您  春香姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.28,0:08:24.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起留宿啊  睡衣聚會呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.28,0:08:27.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃  不  只是完成作業而已
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.18,0:08:31.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋  睡衣聚會是哪個國家的節日呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.30,0:08:34.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少我不認為那是什麼節日之類
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.18,0:08:36.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼時候啊  睡衣節
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.53,0:08:39.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…今天…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.14,0:08:40.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.69,0:08:43.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是突然啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.46,0:08:44.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.59,0:08:47.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少也留出一週的時間讓我們準備吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.98,0:08:51.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又不是什麼節日  只是大家一起完成作業而已
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.42,0:08:56.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我說啊春香  作為主人  總是要準備一點什麼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.38,0:08:57.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主人？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.82,0:09:01.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼就讓我來把這次盛典搞得火熱吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.70,0:09:03.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…到底能不能來呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.24,0:09:05.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.05,0:09:08.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我該做一些準備工作了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.48,0:09:14.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就算了  夏奈  乖乖給我坐在這裡！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.30,0:09:16.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃  可是準備…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.49,0:09:19.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你最好不要跟今天的盛典扯上關係
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.62,0:09:21.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.33,0:09:24.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不想被你那些鬼點子給耍了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.21,0:09:26.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個慶典要由我來主辦！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.39,0:09:28.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是讓客人感覺到無趣了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.90,0:09:30.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們南家的顏面何存！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.95,0:09:32.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以都說了不是什麼盛典
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.69,0:09:34.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是完成作業而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.44,0:09:37.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  今天晚上就吃火鍋吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.29,0:09:38.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好有好多人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.88,0:09:41.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不錯啊  火鍋  一家團聚的基礎啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.94,0:09:44.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好  飯菜也由我來操辦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.54,0:09:49.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我出門買東西了  你們在家好好看門啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.58,0:09:52.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香姐姐  一路小心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.08,0:09:57.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火鍋…團聚…家庭
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.51,0:10:01.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  我也開始準備…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.83,0:10:12.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說隔壁的鄰居搬進來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.62,0:10:13.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.99,0:10:15.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是個什麼樣的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.62,0:10:16.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.08,0:10:18.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不關心嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.62,0:10:19.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.79,0:10:21.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是冷淡的說法呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.82,0:10:24.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今後可能會經常見面
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.83,0:10:27.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不覺得應該先去打個招呼比較好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.33,0:10:29.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣想的話你自己去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.50,0:10:30.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.34,0:10:36.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說來這打招呼是年長者該做的事情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.92,0:10:38.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以是春香的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.95,0:10:42.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然沒有資格說別人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.83,0:10:46.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過既然你都這麼說了  不覺得自己很沒責任感嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.72,0:10:51.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定我們這麼說話的時候  對方已經過來打招呼了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.92,0:10:53.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.80,0:10:56.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.23,0:10:58.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.71,0:10:59.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這倆傢伙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.56,0:11:01.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早知道就不開門了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.97,0:11:02.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.85,0:11:04.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要在意  進門吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.23,0:11:06.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.48,0:11:07.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  阿珍
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.12,0:11:08.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.43,0:11:10.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼事情嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.01,0:11:13.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘁  跟我過來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.04,0:11:18.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是不明白你的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.79,0:11:20.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是這打扮很奇怪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.75,0:11:21.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.08,0:11:23.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好考慮下TPO
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.08,0:11:23.90,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（TPO：分別代表時間（Time）、場合（Occasion）和地點（Place），\N即著裝應該與當時的時間、所處的場合和地點相協調。）
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.88,0:11:27.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  還是PTO來著…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.25,0:11:38.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.15,0:11:40.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙來做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.09,0:11:42.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼PTA之類
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.12,0:11:44.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.34,0:11:45.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.77,0:11:48.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真舒服呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.39,0:11:51.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼千秋家就這麼舒適呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.89,0:11:52.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.88,0:11:55.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是享樂異世界嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.63,0:11:57.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我再躺一會兒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.68,0:11:59.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我肚子餓了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.61,0:12:02.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說  可沒有時間那麼悠閒了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.62,0:12:03.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.69,0:12:06.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了好了  趕緊換衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.65,0:12:08.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這才五點剛過…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.30,0:12:11.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼呢  盛典已經開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.11,0:12:16.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盛典是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.54,0:12:18.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是祭典啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.13,0:12:21.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿…嘿…嘿…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.84,0:12:20.74,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.44,0:12:23.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  準備操辦的人回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.84,0:12:27.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好半路遇見  於是就讓他們幫忙提東西回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.68,0:12:29.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.68,0:12:30.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.60,0:12:34.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你  馬上就準備好了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.33,0:12:35.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來幫你的忙  春香姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.76,0:12:41.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.91,0:12:45.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼你會在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.07,0:12:47.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒  應邀啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.96,0:12:48.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰邀你來的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.20,0:12:50.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我叫他來的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.07,0:12:51.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.11,0:12:54.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個跟藤岡沒有關係吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.29,0:12:56.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為今天不是要吃火鍋嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.72,0:12:58.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是被火鍋所召喚來的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.97,0:13:01.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃  我並不這麼認為
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.15,0:13:04.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋  這是怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.96,0:13:08.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼怎麼  夏奈又開始犯蠢了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.12,0:13:10.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然連床都鋪好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.88,0:13:12.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,動作真迅速啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.35,0:13:14.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就知道做無聊的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.49,0:13:16.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏奈她也想加入的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.83,0:13:19.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她要是想加入的話早就自己跑進來加入了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.57,0:13:21.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.72,0:13:23.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說  你們怎麼都換好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.77,0:13:25.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連床都鋪好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.06,0:13:28.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不趕緊換衣服的話會被罵的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.96,0:13:29.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.14,0:13:31.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人都來齊了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.78,0:13:35.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  冬馬  為什麼不換睡衣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.19,0:13:38.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有帶睡衣來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.88,0:13:42.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有正裝的話會很為難的  客人先生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.78,0:13:44.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手  住手
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.11,0:13:46.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我住手  你這個性騷擾大嬸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.73,0:13:50.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼你比任何人都這麼在意睡衣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.36,0:13:54.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你看  我們不是主人嗎  不是要招待客人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.97,0:13:58.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非你因為是妹妹的聚會
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.28,0:14:00.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以不好意思直接說自己要加入嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.89,0:14:02.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以加入嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.32,0:14:06.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.83,0:14:07.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.50,0:14:10.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.59,0:14:13.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.16,0:14:15.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我就弱弱地奉送一句
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.63,0:14:19.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是要留宿  才五點就穿睡衣太早了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.74,0:14:20.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這該死的！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.71,0:14:30.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茶碗…是這個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.23,0:14:32.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  就用那個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.32,0:14:32.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.28,0:14:35.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  這裡的也可以用嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.11,0:14:35.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.26,0:14:36.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.33,0:14:38.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火鍋
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.29,0:14:41.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  火鍋的話已經拿過去了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.43,0:14:46.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我們開始吃火鍋吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.39,0:14:48.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次火鍋聚會由我來主持
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.69,0:14:50.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都沒有意見吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.73,0:14:55.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最開始是肉類和魚  放進去的時候要注意
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.07,0:14:58.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂喂  你在做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.19,0:15:00.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然差不多的話就一起進去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.26,0:15:04.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗚…我理想的火鍋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.25,0:15:07.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.51,0:15:08.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.47,0:15:10.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,韭菜和生菜也要放進去的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.00,0:15:13.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃  好的…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.53,0:15:17.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.78,0:15:32.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.50,0:15:37.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了來了  誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.78,0:15:39.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼晚了來打擾您真是不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.03,0:15:44.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我剛剛搬來隔壁  所以來拜訪您
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.65,0:15:46.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫冬木
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.62,0:15:48.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新來的？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.80,0:15:49.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好沉我說
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.42,0:15:52.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他大概是長子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.10,0:15:54.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都說了你很沉！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.52,0:15:56.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是很有禮貌的少年呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.11,0:15:57.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧  千秋
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.06,0:16:00.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多給我閃開吧你  蠢貨
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.63,0:16:03.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  這是給您的一點小意思
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.80,0:16:06.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  真是勞您費心了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.27,0:16:08.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得是羊羹
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.86,0:16:10.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概是毛巾或者肥皂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.84,0:16:13.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我適可而止  蠢貨
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.74,0:16:16.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您在招待客人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.18,0:16:20.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃  不過實際上是我們家的孩子在鬧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.18,0:16:23.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  要是還沒有吃晚飯的話一起來吃吧怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.78,0:16:26.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.30,0:16:29.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我爸爸已經做好晚飯了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.47,0:16:31.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係沒關係  就在這裡吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.14,0:16:35.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃  真的不用了  我先告辭了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.76,0:16:40.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  春香  那傢伙是長子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.99,0:16:44.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說是跟他爸爸兩個人住在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.47,0:16:47.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起來是一個很不錯的傢伙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.54,0:16:49.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.09,0:16:55.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好飽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.74,0:16:57.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很難看的  不要這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.82,0:16:59.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會被藤岡同學看見的喲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.96,0:17:04.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不愧是春香  作為主人招待得真完美
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.05,0:17:06.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全沒有在聽
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.20,0:17:11.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可別去搗亂  大家都是來寫作業的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.89,0:17:15.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可不是搗亂  這是招待啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.71,0:17:21.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼睛好疼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.94,0:17:26.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不要去理會夏奈  她只會添亂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.65,0:17:30.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼只提醒我呢  跟大家說
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.04,0:17:33.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不是因為你是最讓人擔心的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.43,0:17:35.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.25,0:17:39.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要交換嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.45,0:17:41.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.78,0:17:56.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.63,0:17:58.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.07,0:18:00.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃  沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.24,0:18:05.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.15,0:18:06.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.99,0:18:08.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很像阿珍呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.45,0:18:12.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.33,0:18:18.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓他們四個人一起洗澡？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.79,0:18:21.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咱家的澡盆有那麼大嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.26,0:18:24.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個澡盆大概勉強可以擠進去三個人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.47,0:18:26.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.79,0:18:31.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真想要一個可以悠閒地洗澡的浴室呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.91,0:18:32.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.82,0:18:36.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看看誰先泡昏…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.60,0:18:37.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比賽…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.79,0:18:44.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小…想要…比賽？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.68,0:18:45.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.85,0:18:48.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小…比賽
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.44,0:18:50.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小…想要
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.81,0:18:51.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靈感來了！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.45,0:18:55.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的招待就是…牛奶！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.90,0:18:59.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們一定會心存感激喝下這牛奶的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.07,0:18:59.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.49,0:19:03.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香  什麼是招待？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.14,0:19:05.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是細心地招待！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.11,0:19:08.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本沒有我考慮的餘地
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.18,0:19:10.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要通過細心照顧來引導他們
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.40,0:19:13.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了這個  我去燒洗澡水
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.12,0:19:16.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  洗澡水已經燒好了的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.52,0:19:18.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂～來試試新的香皂吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.86,0:19:19.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.24,0:19:23.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒  你還真的是…嘿嘿嘿
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.42,0:19:25.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈  有不要臉的色大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.20,0:19:27.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你給我滾出去！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.51,0:19:34.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底誰是最成熟的呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.62,0:19:45.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我使浴室燃燒了！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.97,0:19:48.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後再及時送牛奶去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.95,0:19:54.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.59,0:19:55.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多謝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.89,0:19:59.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起來似乎是變熱鬧了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.42,0:20:01.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…哈
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.02,0:20:07.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  內田  你第一個洗完了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.91,0:20:09.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要喝點牛奶？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.65,0:20:11.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  我就不客氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.87,0:20:15.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再來一杯！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.45,0:20:18.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可會喝壞肚子的喲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.88,0:20:25.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  千秋  要不要喝點牛奶？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.89,0:20:29.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們在做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.04,0:20:32.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  好熱  口渴死了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.24,0:20:35.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼可以喝的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.19,0:20:36.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  那個是…牛奶？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.05,0:20:39.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有水果味兒的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.16,0:20:40.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我睡覺去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.34,0:20:41.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.50,0:20:42.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我差不多也該…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.10,0:20:45.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  沒有睡衣的傢伙回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.75,0:20:46.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.03,0:20:48.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都有喜歡的人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.55,0:20:49.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.32,0:20:52.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夜晚這才剛剛開始
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.33,0:20:54.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還要繼續下去哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.20,0:20:56.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你給我適可而止
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.83,0:20:59.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼  接下來是大人的時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.82,0:21:01.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小孩子禁止進入喔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.10,0:21:04.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼標準？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.55,0:21:06.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼標準的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.55,0:21:12.56,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（有一點兒  算是有  有） 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.56,0:21:15.77,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（一點都沒有）
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.09,0:21:15.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…「有」和「沒有」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.01,0:21:17.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拒絕接受這個標準
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.23,0:21:19.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬馬不是男的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.22,0:21:21.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼  我可是女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.49,0:21:22.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是男孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.82,0:21:25.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.58,0:21:29.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又來了  真是  放開我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.80,0:21:31.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少比千秋更女生
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.10,0:21:31.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煩死了！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.44,0:21:34.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多給我睡覺去！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.24,0:21:37.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼  睡衣盛典現在才剛剛開始
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.83,0:21:42.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家  該起床了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.84,0:21:46.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  真是充實的一個盛典呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.34,0:21:48.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  真的很開心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.42,0:21:49.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還想再來一次
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.23,0:21:53.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以啊  只要那個蠢貨不在的話
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.48,0:21:54.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.76,0:21:57.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後  大家作業都做得怎麼樣了？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.40,0:23:31.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家知道秋天的七草嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.92,0:23:34.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胡枝子  芒草  葛花  瞿麥  敗醬草  蘭草  桔梗
